                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 437.00/49.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-03-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 27, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Cuban Senate yesterday approved House arbitration bill quoted in my No. 655
                    of March 18.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Beaupré</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
